commit.message:
Add files via upload

This is what we used to get data for the entire year for a particular artist.

It produces 365 json files, each labelled with their particular date.

These json files are faster to use to glean information than pulling every time.

After use, the json files were organized into folders by artist.

Process can be (and was) repeated for different days until the desired artist is found
